<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1211</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qīng chén de shí hòu wǒ dēng shàng shǒu wàng lóu, jǔ mù tiào wàng mǎng mǎng de shén zhōu.
 tǔ de féi wò shān hé jǐn xiù, chù chù dōu shì dà fēng shōu. hǎo jì
 jié hǎo shí hòu, wǒ men tóng xīn wèi zhōng guó qí qiú. hǎo jì
 jié hǎo shí hòu, nán de de hé shuǐ yǐ jīng fù liú.</lyrics>
<title>dēng shàng shǒu wàng lóu 迦南1211</title>
</song>